name: Top Down Sketchy BW Game Assets (256x256)
name_original: Top Down Sketchy BW Game Assets (256x256)
description:
Free game assets (256x256 pixels) in sketchy black and white style for your game. Originally done for my class project and since I have no more use to it, feel free to use it. Included in this set:  dungeon walls, maze path, tiles, bushes, small plants, and some small items. 

Credits are not required but will be appreciated. If you decided to credit, please credit `Hachiretsu` as the artist and attach the link to your project in the comment, I would love to see it. :)
